name: Generica Icon Set
description:
Generica is a fully editable icon set of 250 ready to use icons in a modern line style.


  • Made with care. Each icon is hand crafted with the same visually consistent, high quality design style in mind.
  • Clean and consistent. Generica Icon Set is clean and consistent not very stylized to fit any project any project
  • Organized. The set is neatly organized in categories including:
  • Essentials
  • Files and Folders
  • Dialog
  • Users
  • Media
  • Devices
  • Connectivity
  • Finance
  • Arrows
